<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<!-- Header with image -->
<header class="w3-container w3-center w3-padding-32">
    <br>
     <h1 class="title, text-center"> 课程列表</h1>
     <p><span class="w3-tag" style="background-color:grey">夏季课程</span></p>
</header>

<body>


<!-- Grid -->
<div class="w3-row">
  <% @products.each_with_index do |product, index| %>

  <!--=== 商品列表 ===-->
<div class="w3-col l8 s12">
  <%= link_to product_path(product) do %>
  <div class="w3-card-4 w3-margin w3-white">
    <!-- 商品圖片 -->
    <% if product.image.present? %>
      <%= image_tag(product.image.thumb.url, class: "thumbnail") %>
    <% else %>
      <%= image_tag('http://placehold.it/200x200&text=No Pic', class: 'thumbnail') %>
    <% end %>
    <% end %>

    <!-- <img src="/w3images/woods.jpg" alt="Nature" style="width:100%"> -->
    <!-- 商品信息 -->
    <div class="w3-container">
      <h3><b><%= link_to(product.title , product_path(product)) %></b></h3>
      <h5>Title description, <span class="w3-opacity">$<%= product.price %></span></h5>
    </div>

    <div class="w3-container">
      <p>Mauris neque quam, fermentum ut nisl vitae, convallis maximus nisl. Sed mattis nunc id lorem euismod placerat. Vivamus porttitor magna enim, ac accumsan tortor cursus at. Phasellus sed ultricies mi non congue ullam corper. Praesent tincidunt sed
